wiki.summary: “Jump” is a song by Tyla, Gunna and Skillibeng. In the song, Tyla is unapologetically herself, whether that be in her skills of dancing, or being proud of her ethnicity, and hometown ; Johannesburg, South Africa. Jump is track 9 of Tyla’s eponymous studio album. The track then became viral on Tiktok, following it’s March 22nd, 2024 release, with 100,000 videos under the sound at the time, becoming one of the millions of trends on the app. Read more on Last.fm.
